WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:04.000
Repository work inside one terminal.

00:04.000 --> 00:11.000
Ask for one focused repository change.

00:11.000 --> 00:16.000
Review the exact diff before writing.

00:16.000 --> 00:36.000
Approve once. Sigil applies the edit and verifies the result.

00:36.000 --> 00:41.000
Resume the saved repository session later.

00:41.000 --> 00:45.000
Install the Sigil alpha and open it in your repository.
